title: State of git-annex operations on Win10
body:
After a not very promising exploration of the state of things under WSL1 and WSL2 (regarding access to files within the VM from the Windows world) I tried to explore the state of native operations. I performed this installation procedure https://github.com/datalad-handbook/book/issues/132 wit the aim to have something as simple as possible with the least number of configuration steps and different environments to take care off.

<summary>Here is a full log of `git annex test` on a recent "Windows Insider" build (`10.0.18965 Build18965`)

92 out of 168 tests failed (162.26s)

"Zugriff verweigert" is German for "permission denied"

</summary>
